<L>__{exterior los angeles streets 6th and wall night}
<A>__{chris walking among the hordes of homeless at 6th and wall streets. open fires burn in front of cardboard shacks. there are blacks, whites, mexicans, even families with children, junkies, winos, hustlers, and hookers.}
<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{exterior los angeles streets broadway night}
<A>__{new angle: chris walking down broadway. this is clearly just blocks away from where we last saw him, yet the atmosphere is as if of a different world. one of those downtown la hip yuppie blocks. he comes upon a bar. through the window chris sees young men and women roughly his own age working people, suits, gold chainers. metallica blares on the sound system.}
